<paragraph id="8BBB522EFF9CFFB2C9F5FD7EFA9BB698" blockId="9.[136,1451,597,764]" pageId="9" pageNumber="202">
<emphasis id="B9708E3CFF9CFFB2C9F5FD7EFE10B6BC" bold="true" box="[189,430,701,728]" pageId="9" pageNumber="202">Taxonomic notes:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C0429ADFF9CFFB2C8E6FD7DFD05B6BC" authorityName="Persoon" authorityYear="1806" box="[430,699,702,728]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="9" pageNumber="202" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ophthalmica">
<emphasis id="B9708E3CFF9CFFB2C8E6FD7DFD05B6BC" box="[430,699,702,728]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="202">Euphorbia ophthalmica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is very similar to 
<taxonomicName id="4C0429ADFF9CFFB2CADAFD7DFC57B6BC" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" box="[914,1001,702,728]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="9" pageNumber="202" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hirta">
<emphasis id="B9708E3CFF9CFFB2CADAFD7DFC57B6BC" box="[914,1001,702,728]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="202">E. hirta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
due to the cyathia arranged in capitate synflorescences, but the species differ, mainly, on the position of them (see notes under 
<taxonomicName id="4C0429ADFF9CFFB2CD17FD21FAAAB698" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" box="[1119,1300,738,764]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="9" pageNumber="202" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hirta">
<emphasis id="B9708E3CFF9CFFB2CD17FD21FAAAB698" box="[1119,1300,738,764]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="202">Euphorbia hirta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
